      "content": "those are decent, but they're a bit generic. i'm looking for something more specific to help us decide if they'll actually \"mesh\" with the group on a more personal level. like, our team spends a lot of time together outside of work too—grabbing drinks, traveling, etc. maybe some questions about their lifestyle or how they spend their downtime? i want to make sure their background and social habits won't feel totally out of place with the crew we already have.",
